DENME A MI NIÑA.</i>

976
01:19:11,646 --> 01:19:14,706
DEVUÉLVANMELA.

977
01:19:15,350 --> 01:19:17,818
<i>[ABBEY/ VO Z SUMERIA]
"...- " NIÑA "...- "</i>

978
01:19:19,354 --> 01:19:23,222
<i>[VO Z DE ABBEY]
POR FAVOR, ES MI HIJA</i>

979
01:19:23,291 --> 01:19:26,317
DÉNMELA.

980
01:19:27,095 --> 01:19:31,259
<i>[ABBEY/ VO Z SUMERIA]
NIÑA "...- " NUNCA</i>

981
01:19:31,333 --> 01:19:35,963
